    <section id="fers-supplement" class="fed-ed-ss-section">
      <span class="fed-ed-chapter-label">CHAPTER II: THE BRIDGE</span>
      <h2 class="fed-ed-ss-section-title">FERS Supplement: Your <em>Bridge</em> to 62</h2>
      
      <p class="fed-ed-ss-body">The FERS supplement is federal employees' secret weapon — a special payment that bridges the income gap from retirement until Social Security eligibility at age 62. This benefit can provide $1,200-$2,000 monthly, but it comes with strict eligibility rules and earnings limitations.</p>
      
      <div class="fed-ed-glass-card">
